rows.label: tlk45320152_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The refugees from Acedia are being
housed in this port for the time being.

rows.label: tlk45320152_04_msg0002
rows.name:
But the Superbian Divine Beast too has
grown very weak of late.

rows.label: tlk45320152_04_msg0003
rows.name:
There's no guarantee that anyone
will be safe here for long...

rows.label: tlk45320152_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I just hope they aren't all forced to
flee to another Divine Beast a second time...
